text: Bethanie Mattek-Sands and Lucie Šafářová were the defending champions, but decided not to compete together. Mattek-Sands played alongside Heather Watson, but lost in the quarterfinals to Andreja Klepač and Katarina Srebotnik. Šafářová teamed up with Tímea Babos, but lost in the first round to Kateryna Bondarenko and Olga Savchuk. Ekaterina Makarova and Elena Vesnina won the title, defeating Simona Halep and Monica Niculescu in the final, 6–3, 7–6(7–5). ==Seeds== The top four seeds received a bye into the second round. ==Draw== ===Finals=== ===Top half=== ===Bottom half=== ==References== *Doubles Draw Rogers Cup Doubles Rogers Cup - Women's Doubles Women's Doubles Rogers
